0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","section",null,{"className":"pt-12 pb-16 px-5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#95a5a6] to-[#7f8c8d] text-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-4xl mb-4 block","children":"🟢"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4","children":"省電模式型"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto","children":"你不是吃太多，你是吃太少太久了。"}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#2a2520] border-l-4 pl-5 font-semibold mb-8","style":{"borderLeftColor":"#7f8c8d"},"children":"當你反覆少吃，身體以為你在鬧飢荒。它的反應是：降低基礎代謝率、分解肌肉當燃料、每一口食物都被高效率地存成脂肪。你越努力少吃，身體就越努力幫你存。"}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"pb-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-12","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"🧠"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"你的身體發生了什麼事？"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"你的身體是一台非常聰明的機器。當它發現「食物供應不穩定」——也就是你反覆節食、少吃——它會啟動一個叫做「代謝適應」的生存機制。\n\n這個機制在幾萬年前是救命的。當食物不夠的時候，身體會做三件事來幫你活下去：\n\n第一，降低基礎代謝率。就像手機電量低的時候會自動進入省電模式——關掉不必要的功能，用最少的電撐最久。\n\n第二，分解肌肉當燃料。肌肉是身體裡最耗能的組織，省電模式下第一個被「裁員」的就是它。肌肉少了，你每天能消耗的熱量就更低。\n\n第三，提高食物的儲存效率。每一口食物都被身體高效率地轉換成脂肪存起來。"}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"❌"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"為什麼常見方法對你沒用？"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"「吃更少」對省電模式型來說，是最糟糕的建議。\n\n每一次新的節食計畫——168 斷食、生酮、水煮餐、代餐——都是在告訴你的身體：「又來了，又要鬧飢荒了！」身體的反應就是把省電模式調得更低、存得更多。\n\n這就是「越減越胖」的科學原理。你的基礎代謝可能已經被壓到遠低於正常值。別人一天能消耗 1500 卡，你可能只剩 1000 卡。就算你只吃 1200 卡，多出來的 200 卡照樣被存成脂肪。\n\n數學很殘酷，但問題不在你，在方法。"}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#eee9e5]","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"💡"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold","children":"那怎麼辦？"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-base leading-[1.8] text-[#2a2520] whitespace-pre-line","children":"你需要做的事情聽起來很違反直覺：吃夠。\n\n不是暴吃，而是讓身體知道「飢荒結束了，可以正常運轉了」。\n\n第一步是吃夠蛋白質。蛋白質是重建肌肉的材料，而肌肉是你的代謝引擎。引擎修好了，每天能燒的熱量才會回來。\n\n第二步是慢慢把熱量吃回來。不是一夜之間從 1000 卡跳到 1800 卡，而是循序漸進，讓身體逐步信任「食物是穩定的」。\n\n第三步是加入適當的阻力訓練。不需要去健身房操到爆——在家做幾組深蹲、推牆伏地挺身就夠了。"}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-8 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-[#fef8ee] border-l-4 border-[#f39c12] rounded-r-xl p-6 text-[17px] font-semibold leading-relaxed","children":"你已經夠努力了。現在需要的不是更嚴格的計畫，是一套「讓身體解除省電模式」的策略——從吃夠、睡好、慢慢重建代謝引擎開始。"}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-12 px-5","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold mb-6","children":["💡 給","省電模式","的你"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","div","0",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#7f8c8d"},"children":1}],"不要再逼自己少吃了。你已經夠努力了，身體需要的是營養，不是飢餓。"]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#7f8c8d"},"children":2}],"吃夠蛋白質。肌肉是你的代謝引擎，保住肌肉才保得住代謝。"]}],"$L2"]}]]}]}],"$L3","$L4"],["$L5"],"$L6"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"uQOx9nQ91OA0_aB4689wt"}
2:["$","div","2",{"className":"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-[#eee9e5] text-[15px] leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-bold mr-2","style":{"backgroundColor":"#7f8c8d"},"children":3}],"如果「少吃」有用，你早就瘦了。所以答案一定在別的地方——比如「吃夠」。"]}]
